c-advisory-services-international-humanitarian-law" title="">国际人道法咨询服务处</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/what-we-do/building-respect-ihl/education-outreach" title="">教授与学习国际人道法</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/law-and-policy" title="">法律与政策论坛</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/observation-and-opinion" title="">观察与思考</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/humanitarium" title="">活动与参观</a></li></ul></li><li><h5 class="h5">法律议题</h5><ul><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl" title="">当前国际人道法热点问题</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/protected-persons" title="">受保护的人</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/weapons" title="">武器</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/conduct-hostilities" title="">敌对行为</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/emblem" title="">标志的使用</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/international-criminal-jurisdiction" title="">违反国际人道法</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/ihl-domestic-law" title="">国内法与国际人道法</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/ihl-other-legal-regimes" title="">与国际人道法相关的法律体系</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/strengthening-ihl" title="">加强国际人道法的遵守</a></li></ul></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="nav-support-us nav-link-main-container"> <a class="nav-link-main" href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/support-us">支持我们</a><div class="nav-submenu"> <a class="nav-link-sub-toggle i-arrow-left js_toggle visible-sm visible-xs" data-target=".nav-main">返回</a> <a class="nav-link-spot i-arrow-right-after" href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/support-us">概述 支持我们</a><div class=" nav-split"><ul><li><h5 class="h5">立即捐款</h5><ul><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/donate?t=MONTHLY" title="">每月捐款</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/donate" title="为我们的一般资金呼吁捐款">带来希望的捐助</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/donate/covid-19-emergency-appeal" title="">新冠肺炎疫情紧急呼吁</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/donate/syria-crisis-appeal" title="为在叙利亚挽救生命而捐款">为叙利亚危机捐款</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/donate/yemen-crisis-appeal" title="">也门危机资金呼吁</a></li></ul></li><li> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/support-us/where-does-your-money-go" title="">您的捐款被用在何处？</a></li><li> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/faq/donate-by-bank-transfer-or-cheque" title="如何通过银行汇款、邮政汇款或支票为红十字国际委员会捐款">通过银行汇款捐款</a></li><li> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/faq/donate-frequently-asked-questions" title="">向红十字国际委员会捐款：常见问题</a></li><li><h5 class="h5">其他捐款方式</h5><ul><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/support-us/fundraising-event" title="通过组织筹款活动，您将为红十字国际委员会的重要工作提供支持。">为红十字国际委员会筹款</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/support-us/audience/bequests-and-legacies" title="">遗赠和遗产</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/support-us/audience/friends-icrc" title="">红十字国际委员会之友</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/support-us/audience/foundations" title="">与基金会或信托机构合作</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/support-us/audience/philanthropy" title="">进行大额捐款</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/support-us/audience/corporate-support" title="">与公司合作</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/support-us/audience/planned-giving" title="">有计划捐助</a></li></ul></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="nav-donate nav-link-main-container pull-right hidden-xs hidden-sm"> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/donate" class="bg-red nav-link-main">捐款</a></div></div></div></div> </nav></div><div class="region region-content"><div id="fullpage"> <section class="clearfix section first-section " id="what-we-do"><div class="wwd-inner"><div class="header-wrapper visible-sm visible-xs"><header class="site-header"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-4 slogan-logo"><div class="logo-wrapper"><div id="logo"> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh" class="logo"><img src="/sites/default/themes/icrc_theme/images/zh/logo-small.png" alt="红十字国际委员会"/></a></div><div class="slogan font-sm-18"><h1 class="font-sm-18"> 红十字国际委员会</h1></div></div></div><div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-8 right-content"><div class="visible-sm visible-xs list-languages"> <select class="styled-language-select i-arrow-down-after redirection-select"><option value="https://www.icrc.org/zh" selected="selected">ZH</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/en">EN</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/fr">FR</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/es">ES</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/pt">PT</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/ar">AR</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/ru">RU</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/de">DE</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/it">IT</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/en/languages">其他</option> </select></div></div></div></div></header></div><div class="fill section-first-main"><div class="video-section"><div class="video-wrapper responsive-video-container video-available"> <video data-keepplaying data-autoplay loop muted poster="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/special_page_image/public/homepage_files/icrc-car-syria_1.jpg?itok=sydI4NeT"> <source data-src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/homepage_files/what-we-do-video_0.mp4" type="video/mp4" /> </video><div class="image"> <img src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/special_page_image/public/homepage_files/icrc-car-syria_1.jpg?itok=sydI4NeT" alt="icrc-car-syria"/></div><div class="video-text-wrapper"><div class="video-text"> <a href="/zh/what-we-do/video" class="lightbox-embed-video youku"><span class="thumbnail-video-button"></span></a><div class="main-text">在90多个国家开展一线工作——中立、公正、独立——我们是红十字国际委员会</div></div></div></div></div><div class="text-section"><div class="container fill"><div class="row fill"><div class="text-wrapper-outer fill"><div class="text-wrapper"><div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 text-block"> <a class="title-text" href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/who-we-are" class="">了解我们</a><div class="red-divider"></div><div class="sub-text"><p>我们在世界各地为受冲突和武装暴力局势影响的民众提供援助，并推广<a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/the-rules-of-war">战争规则</a>。</p></div></div><div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 text-block"> <a class="title-text" href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/who-we-are/jobs" class="">加入我们</a><div class="red-divider"></div><div class="sub-text"><p>你有从事人道工作的意愿吗？进一步了解如何加入红十字国际委员会。</p></div></div><div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 text-block"> <a class="title-text" href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/support-us" class="">支持我们</a><div class="red-divider"></div><div class="sub-text"><p>帮助世界各地受武装冲突影响的家庭和社区。</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section> <section class="clearfix section ss " id="highlight"><div class="fill "><div class="video-section no-video-available"> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/document/syria-economic-crisis-bites-lack-humanitarian-access-costs-lives-every-day" target="_self" ><div class="highlight-image-wrapper"><div class="image " style="background-image: url('https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/special_page_image/public/home_carousel_slide/image/20200202_ammar_saboh_-_harasta-7_0.jpg?itok=qLpseX8O');"></div></div> </a><div class="highlight-text-wrapper"><div class="highlight-text-inner JsClickParent" data-ClickLink="https://www.icrc.org/zh/document/syria-economic-crisis-bites-lack-humanitarian-access-costs-lives-every-day"> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/document/syria-economic-crisis-bites-lack-humanitarian-access-costs-lives-every-day" target="_self" class="highlight-title" ><span class="crnr-brdr crnr-brdr-tl"></span>叙利亚经济恶化 人道援助通道不畅加剧危机<span class="crnr-brdr crnr-brdr-br"></span></a><div class="highlight-fields JsClickParent" data-ClickLink="https://www.icrc.org/zh/document/syria-economic-crisis-bites-lack-humanitarian-access-costs-lives-every-day"><div class="highlight-share hidden-sm hidden-xs JsClickParent" d