态：16名平民医疗后送至迈杜古里接受外科治疗</a><div class="date">2020-06-15</div></li><li> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/document/sudan-humanitarian-aid-flight-brings-medical-and-support-staff-khartoum">苏丹：人道援助航班为喀土穆送来医务和支援人员</a><div class="date">2020-06-09</div></li></ol></div></div></div></div><div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-6"><div class="media-links-top media-box"> <a class ="media-link media-link-contact" href='https://www.icrc.org/zh/contact#media-contacts'><div class="tb"><div class="tc"><span class="icon i-contact"></span>媒体联系人</div></div> </a> <a class ="media-link media-link-newroom" href='http://www.icrcnewsroom.org/'><div class="tb"><div class="tc"><span class="icon i-document-type-4"></span>视频新闻室</div></div> </a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col-md-12 col-lg-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 mob-land-50 float-left"><div class="media-tweets media-box"><div class="social-icon-container"><div class="social-icon-row"> <a class="social-icon i-wechat-large" href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/document/china-wechat-qr-code" target="_blank"><span class="sr-only">Wechat</span></a> <a class="social-icon i-sina-weibo-large" href="http://www.weibo.com/icrc" target="_blank"><span class="sr-only">新浪微博</span></a> <a class="social-icon i-youku-large" href="http://i.youku.com/u/UNzY1MzQ2NDg=" target="_blank"><span class="sr-only">优酷</span></a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="container media-links-bottom hidden-lg hidden-md"><div class="row"><div class="media-links-bottom-wrapper"><div class="media-link-bottom media-resource"> <a class ="media-link" href='https://www.icrc.org/zh/media-room'> <span class="icon i-document-type-7"></span>最新资讯 </a></div><div class="media-link-bottom media-contact"> <a class ="media-link" href='https://www.icrc.org/zh/contact#media-contacts'> <span class="icon i-contact"></span>媒体联系人 </a></div><div class="media-link-bottom media-newsroom"> <a class ="media-link" href='http://www.icrcnewsroom.org/'> <span class="icon i-document-type-4"></span>视频新